{"tid":1791943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]快速入門，教你如何用Twitter","createTime":"2019-12-21T08:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:07:27.000Z","uid":217413,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6eeb44f2369a52c7ce89a3644dccc5db59d2cce9","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"我玩開Twitter用咗差唔多4年<br />\n冇諗過原來好多人唔識用Twitter，當係fb ig咁用<br />\n咁作為一個用慣Twitter嘅人想教下大家有咩技巧<br />\nTwitter都有獨特嘅生態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事先講明，依個po係教你點樣用得好，唔係點樣開始用，account都未開嘅可以去搵其他教學先返黎睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. Twitter有字數限制</span><br />\n開始用Twitter嘅人應該好快發現，但我都想講下字數限制<br />\n每個Tweet都限制140字(280字符)以內<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以一定要簡潔</span><br />\n如果點刪減都係過字數，有兩個建議方法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一，係comment繼續打</span><br />\n  最頂頂嘅Tweet喺開頭寫1)，回覆就打2)，如此類推，又或者你預先知道自己要分成幾多段先打得哂，可以用分數開頭(例如分三段就1/3, 2/3, 3/3)直到寫哂你想講嘅野；日文嘅話就係每段未完嘅文字寫(続く，否則好多人都唔知道你回覆度仲有下續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但壞處係大部分人習慣只會RT(retweet)最頂嘅Tweet<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二，直接將你想講嘅野整成圖片Tweet</span><br />\n  RT數就會集中，但壞處係關鍵字搵唔到，事實上玩開Twitter嘅人唔係次次都用hashtag搜，有時係會用關鍵字搜<br />\n<br />\n所以如無必要，<span style=\"color: red;\">都盡可能用一個Tweet過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 用hashtag</span><br />\n大家都識用，我唔詳細講<br />\n我比較想提嘅係，如果你要打大段文，但hashtag又佔字數，唔好貪心，<span style=\"color: red;\">建議只用5個tag或以下</span><br />\n你係回覆po哂所有有關hashtag，啲人搜tag就會只睇到你個充滿hashtag嘅回覆，人係懶架，除非好得閒/好有興趣，唔係嘅話係唔會click入去睇原本你打嘅係咩<br />\n用唔同嘅tag tweet多幾次，唔好懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但記住唔好打同一樣野，Twitter會當成spam，自動隱藏你啲文</span><br />\n其他人搜tag見到咁多一模一樣嘅野都會覺得好L煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. No spam</span><br />\n繼續上面講嘅野，唔spam咁可以點tweet好多野<br />\n大家唔好當成fb ig，<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter係一個好適合發廢文嘅平台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你打&ldquo;好攰呀&rdquo;一個Tweet，又打&ldquo;今日早訓，早抖&rdquo;另發一個新tweet，甚至你打OMG、啊啊啊啊啊、一個emoji，<span style=\"color: red;\">喺Twitter度都好常見架</span><br />\n當然我唔係叫大家發廢文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你諗唔到好多篇唔同嘅文，打一句感想、再加hashtag，咁就搞掂架啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子：It was pouring but I still went to Victoria Park for the protest. Hongkongers were very nice. (加hashtag)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 刷RT數</span><br />\n要刷RT數就要集中係一個Tweet，唔好諗住啲人會瘋狂RT所有有關嘅Tweet<br />\n另外，冇咩follower嘅人嘅Tweet基本上好少人會睇到，更加唔好講會RT，可以收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你哋可以RT多啲多follower嘅推主啲Tweet(例如Gphone、所羅門、攬炒、周庭、Rie&hellip;&hellip;以及個名隔離有✔嘅係官方帳號，都可以多啲推)<br />\n好多新手會用RT with comment，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係RT with comment唔會刷到RT數</span><br />\n好殘忍，刷RT數係必然要做，<span style=\"color: red;\">其他人見到數字大先會RT而唔係留心心就走</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋如果推主冇更改通知設定，佢直頭會係通知欄見到你RT with comment打咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有善用RT數高嘅Tweet，如果有特別資訊同消息想多啲人知道，除咗搵多follower嘅人幫手，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦可以直接係下面回個覆，好過你發個唔知有冇十條友睇過嘅新Tweet多多聲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人見到反應熱烈、回覆數多啲Tweet，都會click入去睇埋comment架<br />\n因為我就係其中一位會咁做嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5. 與五毛大軍對戰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直接port鳩佢哋個account同相關推文啦</span>，尤其是喺人哋留言搞事嗰班<br />\nClick埋入五毛個timeline，順手檢舉埋其他有問題嘅Tweet<br />\n我呢幾個月都舉報咗唔少，有啲仲收到通知，我檢舉嘅帳戶被確認違反Twitter規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於hashtag帶風向，相信大家都識點做，所以我唔係度再講啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外提提大家</span></span><br />\n大家想保障自己私隱嘅話，記得係設定&rarr;可搜尋性和聯絡人&rarr;讓其他人透過電話找到你&rarr;整走個剔，唔好比人用手機number搵到你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YDdUFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YDdUFJ.jpg&h=6d542309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n上一個po好多人會有嘅疑問：<br />\nQ. 我應該follow咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA. 首先一定要follow重要人物嘅ac，例如侵侵、眾議員、參議員&hellip;&hellip;但為免被Twitter以為係bot，唔好淨係follow呢類ac<br />\n有巴打話可以follow啲貓貓ac，Retweet下啲貓貓相，會易啲吸引人follow你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲可以search #手足互科，你會搵到好多巴絲打嘅ac，你可以follow佢哋，同佢哋say 個hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ. RT+reply同RT with comment有咩分別？<br />\nA. reply：follower未必睇到，但你個回覆會出現喺原文下面，所以其他人都可以睇到你回覆咗啲咩<br />\nRT with comment：會直接出現係你嘅follower嘅timeline，但唔會出現係原文嘅回覆欄度，所以除非咁啱其他人搜尋到你，唔係嘅話，理論上得follower會見到你寫咩<br />\n共通點係兩者都可以被原發文者睇到<br />\n<br />\nQ. 咁我應該用邊個好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA. 如果你好似Gphone嗰啲有好多follower嘅，我建議用RT with comment，如果follower唔算多嘅，我建議用reply。依張&ldquo;Twitter戰線需知&rdquo;好清楚寫咗點解多數會推薦用RT+reply(張圖唔錯所以見到就save低咗，多謝手足製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31ZMvkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31ZMvkv.jpg&h=dc287529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. Follower係咪愈多愈好？係咪要多過xxx人？<br />\nA. 冇人話過超過幾多個follower影響力會大啲，依個係好常見嘅誤解<br />\n而且你嘅follower人數點都唔會多過啲政治人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然唔好得幾丁友follower啦，你follower啲外國人，佢哋睇到你得咁少人follow，會懷疑你係咪只係rt機械人，冇野好睇而唔follow返你<br />\n<br />\nQ. 既然喺出名嘅Account下面留言會有宣傳效果，我係咪reply嘅時候都應該放文宣宣傳？<br />\nA. 唔係，如果你嘅文宣同個tweet嘅內容冇關係，就唔好咁做<br />\n乜都貼文宣，搞到人地個tweet成堆留言都係唔相關嘅文宣，其實好冇禮貌，好易引起其他人反感<br />\n千祈唔好做文宣機械人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家玩Twitter玩得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5395f30b27cb35ca77df718a01457ecb995f1fb","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"舊po<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">快速入門，教你如何用Twitter<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489008</a></span>"},{"pid":"66b0fc841383010fa9b9b3bc2b1acdd3f989fadb","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f688aa79ad26c73668979567bb89a2392f0270e7","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d37f0867ceb4ddcd68cb5a95dbd2b5e3c673f6","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de37d5baa4bec79579e7d59e6446753a11a6e38","tid":1791943,"uid":34116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d277b789f78b69475ee0588b6856284576ede4ab","tid":1791943,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d1cbcd55e76381c423e768283fbc70283179b","tid":1791943,"uid":306684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62bfe5be504427770d282ff1c569a1a6afbfc7e","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50609dc96e294bfc8d4cc01f73dcd272b93d10b9","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17360de6340dcef07f17a5f0ef96c905a31a9862","tid":1791943,"uid":37713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"幫推，唔好再將人地辛辛苦苦譯好既tweet copy &amp; paste啦<br />\n(X) 手動轉<br />\n(O) RT<br />\n你手動轉將原tweet變埋spam message仲得不償失<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste"},{"pid":"fac87a8886ba8b7dbb8c60e4d137a7881eefe684","tid":1791943,"uid":318369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v01K3LM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv01K3LM.jpg&h=33755bd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e104b101839a5e742a34be00addb1773f3d93316","tid":1791943,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"手足借個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pC3mmtL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpC3mmtL.png&h=cd980796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請一個落選區議員， 就拎 $100美金，支爆為止！！</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792362</a>"},{"pid":"fa52f7d4e71a39275da8c4c25ad4be2c7cef3ad5","tid":1791943,"uid":114937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf221cd55c2e5042adc20dcf652f6f965b40483","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17360de6340dcef07f17a5f0ef96c905a31a9862","tid":1791943,"uid":37713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"幫推，唔好再將人地辛辛苦苦譯好既tweet copy &amp; paste啦<br />\n(X) 手動轉<br />\n(O) RT<br />\n你手動轉將原tweet變埋spam message仲得不償失<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"依樣好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該哂手足補充"},{"pid":"3efa7c9074cb3093ffe3bc2e09a65d382682c122","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1779c736c4803e4105f0fe3f1336d73485a89a48","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7ada6fe942aef47346e35d60ee6ef81fb1f8f97","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f0d150ac2e11fd49edb66105cf5563bbf536c95","tid":1791943,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b54b0004b7799fa1acb429b2526875a9a217537a","tid":1791943,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b83fa44ebd5e36b6bf4a02fa12d163c2056f150f","tid":1791943,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df6b92dde152b17a14411c8ed1c290a1438e29c6","tid":1791943,"uid":144463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c719c8387012f8da6b44f71bfbd70abd414ca4e4","tid":1791943,"uid":144463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"359a1ffc5131c93cccab5cbc8367ba6f03d09682","tid":1791943,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T18:30:23.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565c709b2de32b5bc60c9712f74b1fbf65c40197","tid":1791943,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"17360de6340dcef07f17a5f0ef96c905a31a9862","tid":1791943,"uid":37713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"幫推，唔好再將人地辛辛苦苦譯好既tweet copy &amp; paste啦<br />\n(X) 手動轉<br />\n(O) RT<br />\n你手動轉將原tweet變埋spam message仲得不償失<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste<br />\n係RT唔係copy&amp;paste"}}